---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Everybody Everywhere Case Study - Idle Fusion"
  description="How we built a global platform mobilizing millions to pray, give, and share the Gospel with interactive impact tracking."
>
  <Header />

  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="case-hero">
      <div class="case-container">
        <a href="/#our-work" class="back-link">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <path d="M16 10H4M4 10L9 5M4 10L9 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          Back to Work
        </a>

        <div class="case-hero-content">
          <span class="case-category">Faith & Ministry</span>
          <h1 class="case-title">Everybody Everywhere</h1>
          <p class="case-subtitle">A global movement platform mobilizing millions to pray, give, and take the Gospel to every corner of the world.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="case-meta">
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">Client</span>
            <span class="meta-value">Everybody Everywhere</span>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">Industry</span>
            <span class="meta-value">Faith & Ministry</span>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">Platform</span>
            <span class="meta-value">Web Application</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Challenge -->
    <section class="case-section">
      <div class="case-container">
        <div class="section-grid">
          <div class="section-label">
            <span class="label-number">01</span>
            <span class="label-text">The Challenge</span>
          </div>
          <div class="section-content">
            <h2>Unifying a global movement</h2>
            <p>Everybody Everywhere had an ambitious vision: mobilize followers of Jesus worldwide to pray for, give to, and share the Gospel with unreached people groups. But they needed more than a website — they needed a platform that could inspire action and show tangible impact.</p>
            <p>The challenge: create an experience that makes a global mission feel personal, trackable, and achievable — turning passive supporters into active participants.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Approach -->
    <section class="case-section section-alt">
      <div class="case-container">
        <div class="section-grid">
          <div class="section-label">
            <span class="label-number">02</span>
            <span class="label-text">Our Approach</span>
          </div>
          <div class="section-content">
            <h2>Making global feel personal</h2>
            <p>We designed and built a platform centered on engagement and transparency:</p>
            <ul class="approach-list">
              <li><strong>Interactive global map</strong> — Visual exploration of unreached people groups, making the abstract mission concrete and explorable</li>
              <li><strong>Impact tracking dashboard</strong> — Real-time visibility into prayers offered, funds raised, and Gospel shares — showing users their individual contribution to the whole</li>
              <li><strong>Video story integration</strong> — First-person testimonies and field updates that connect supporters emotionally to the mission</li>
              <li><strong>Frictionless giving</strong> — Streamlined donation flow with recurring giving options and transparent fund allocation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Results -->
    <section class="case-section">
      <div class="case-container">
        <div class="section-grid">
          <div class="section-label">
            <span class="label-number">03</span>
            <span class="label-text">The Results</span>
          </div>
          <div class="section-content">
            <h2>A movement activated</h2>
            <div class="results-grid">
              <div class="result-card">
                <span class="result-number">Global</span>
                <span class="result-label">reach across continents</span>
              </div>
              <div class="result-card">
                <span class="result-number">3x</span>
                <span class="result-label">increase in recurring donors</span>
              </div>
              <div class="result-card">
                <span class="result-number">Thousands</span>
                <span class="result-label">of daily active prayers</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>The platform transformed how supporters engage with the mission. Instead of passive donations, users now actively participate — tracking their impact, sharing stories, and inviting others into the movement. The interactive map alone has driven significant increases in time-on-site and return visits.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonial -->
    <section class="case-section section-alt">
      <div class="case-container">
        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p>"The platform Idle Fusion built didn't just meet our technical requirements — it captured the heart of our mission. We've seen unprecedented engagement from our community."</p>
          <cite>— Everybody Everywhere Leadership</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="case-cta">
      <div class="case-container">
        <h2>Have a mission that needs a platform?</h2>
        <p>We specialize in building technology that amplifies impact for faith-based organizations.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Strategy Call</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer variant="minimal" />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .case-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .case-container {
    max-width: 56rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .case-container {
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .case-category {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .case-title {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .case-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 40rem;
  }

  .case-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .meta-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .meta-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .meta-value {
    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .case-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .section-alt {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .section-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .section-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
  }

  .section-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .label-number {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .label-text {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .section-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .section-content p {
    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .approach-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
  }

  .approach-list li {
    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .approach-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .approach-list li strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .results-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .result-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .result-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .result-label {
    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .testimonial {
    max-width: 40rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0;
    border: none;
  }

  .testimonial p {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .testimonial cite {
    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .case-cta {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--ink);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .case-cta h2 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--paper);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .case-cta p {
    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--paper);
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .dark .case-cta {
    background: #0a0a0a;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }
</style>
